NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|As to the auction 2@C was a good bid as was 2N. 3N was a tad of a stretch, but as you know, it is much better, especially in IMPs to play 3N rather than 2N. So I like Gail's 3N call. The only time it is wrong is if they can make exactly 2N and not 3N.|
